---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base
  title="Contact Us | The Life Insider"
  description="Get in touch with The Life Insider team — questions, corrections, and partnership inquiries."
>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container-narrow prose">
      <div class="kicker">Contact</div>
      <h1>Contact Us</h1>

      <p class="lede">
        We read everything. Questions, corrections, product suggestions, and
        partnership inquiries are all welcome.
      </p>

      <div class="card" style="padding: 28px; margin: 24px 0;">
        <h3 style="margin-top:0;">Email us</h3>
        <p style="margin-bottom:0;">
          <a href="mailto:info@thelifeinsider.com"><strong>info@thelifeinsider.com</strong></a><br />
          <span style="color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.9rem;">We aim to respond within 2 business days.</span>
        </p>
      </div>

      <h2>Corrections</h2>
      <p>
        Spotted something inaccurate or out of date — a price, a spec, a
        rating? Email us with the page link and the issue, and we'll review
        and correct it promptly. Accuracy is the product we sell.
      </p>

      <h2>Brands and partnerships</h2>
      <p>
        If you'd like your product considered for review, email us with
        product details and where it's sold. Please note: featuring a product
        is at our discretion, and commercial relationships never change a
        product's Insider Score — see
        <a href="/how-we-rate/">How We Rate</a>.
      </p>

      <h2>Privacy requests</h2>
      <p>
        For data access or deletion requests, see our
        <a href="/privacy/">Privacy Policy</a> and email us with the subject
        line "Privacy Request".
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
